This is yet another writeup of the hermetic paradigm, based on the 
Aristotelian theory of the True Forms. I post it on behalf of 
H.B.DesChenes, whop wrote most of it (I added the bit about Spirit, Time 
and Arete on the end). 

[Strictly speaking, it is the Platonic theory of True Forms]

Date: Sun, 4 Sep 94 16:54:30 -0500
From: hdeschen@lonestar.utsa.edu (Howard B. Des Chenes  )
